{"tid":445013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵年輕情侶","createTime":"2017-10-23T03:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T06:55:47.000Z","uid":58851,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0e62e773e8ae2858286fd32a52e82cb18bec9f31","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"頭先係西鐵見到對後生情侶。<br />\n<br />\n女嘅好青春得黎化晒妝，好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n男嘅後生得黎，留無一吋長極稀疏鬍鬚，一條毛同一條毛之間起碼有4分距離。我完全唔明點解唔剃左佢，或者掹左佢。個頭其他地方似10A麥明詩Ex林作。<br />\n<br />\n女嘅短褲露出白滑長腿。男嘅短褲露出啡密長曲腳毛。<br />\n<br />\n兩個人企係走廊中心，又唔捉扶手。初初我望一望條女，條女就放開捉住男人手臂隻手。但一直玩手機。之後，條仔就係咁想咀條女，但條女唔肯。查實個陣，車廂人多又唔迫。<br />\n<br />\n最從佢地落車個陣，條仔就問，唔肯又點解係答應係埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n我估佢地都係大專生。<br />\n<br />\n我想係度講嘅係，好心條仔想同人一齊就照下鏡先出街啦。我完全睇得出條女係覺得條仔想係庭廣眾表演係影衰佢。連有身體接觸都有咁嘅感覺。條仔又唔係差，但成個頹廢大學生咁，但條女又唔頹。<br />\n<br />\n我相信佢地肯定好快散。"},{"pid":"87fe56dc863e5da8d2335eae004523ce8f8144f5","tid":445013,"uid":25099,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"而你只係企起一邊，得個望字。"},{"pid":"f0eb383d60549cd0130c3a84db9fef953306c02c","tid":445013,"uid":13802,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都鐘意大庭廣眾做親密野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d85391805ed01d9de4865b28a4f44458ef8904","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"Sorry, 我係坐係佢地隔離。"},{"pid":"13c2124c59227f5933e902d7712c097a85a0a6b3","tid":445013,"uid":119379,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"我淨係想睇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212fa70c19f87a45685d240842ddcf67ffc1a279","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係個個都鐘意大庭廣眾做親密野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，可惜條仔好似某d連登仔咁。裝份又毒。又想威。"},{"pid":"4b1eb1b48e4317a49938daff281e6d43a564f830","tid":445013,"uid":67329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"其實，佢地散又好唔散又好都唔關你事喎。"},{"pid":"6773dd468813deef2f4872bb63307597b1a4af2a","tid":445013,"uid":49797,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"浪費左一分鐘睇呢段野"},{"pid":"1058b5196ae4ad9c667f4f679e9722ed7b0294e6","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係想睇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無啦，位置唔好。條女成鬼日盯住我。<br />\n佢影我就無人知。"},{"pid":"15af0c8056f2cfe152029f67091ab238ee5c8ddd","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係想睇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無啦，位置唔好。條女成鬼日盯住我。<br />\n佢影我就無人知。"},{"pid":"d1b30959e0d7c5f4db38c07803fd3c12658f5d03","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係想睇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無啦，位置唔好。條女成鬼日盯住我。<br />\n佢影我就無人知。"},{"pid":"9cdfb2e9e091afb47f56c9061f1fb8571fc045f1","tid":445013,"uid":29790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係個個都鐘意大庭廣眾做親密野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，可惜條仔好似某d連登仔咁。裝份又毒。又想威。</blockquote><br />\n而你就淨係可以開post葡萄?"},{"pid":"5185981c5be8f3f131da2dac3ce864ee1b300a67","tid":445013,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"兵仔黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8a0995c646847e16859817ab1fdf775ea45b05","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實，佢地散又好唔散又好都唔關你事喎。</blockquote><br />\n關。車上少一對危險人物。兩條友都唔扶。"},{"pid":"eb66543ec9faf12cfe05a88f2d6f95ed4e6342e0","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係個個都鐘意大庭廣眾做親密野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，可惜條仔好似某d連登仔咁。裝份又毒。又想威。</blockquote><br />\n而你就淨係可以開post葡萄?</blockquote><br />\n我一d都唔葡萄喎。<br />\n<br />\n係埋一齊但被人望下就掂都唔比掂。<br />\n咁都要葡萄？"},{"pid":"e64a3435a41494a077156d6362e89920e475a91d","tid":445013,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兵仔黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意你講法，返學放學有個傻人係身邊。<br />\n<br />\n假期就話要返工。實質做咩無人知。"},{"pid":"2ff4d8f82ad697b05e190470db2fa553a0827e9b","tid":445013,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"hello moto"},{"pid":"3535acdfff412b324f2f8b4027093e708e35f79b","tid":445013,"uid":67392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"原來係你 你望夠我條女未"},{"pid":"a07c00867ec6c0b4b9730515f452b2de279d087b","tid":445013,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"我屌你老味呀 無圖 <br />\n無圖開咩post呀"},{"pid":"886e3fda560fe8f384b45ef7258b549655e7be4b","tid":445013,"uid":71703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"樓主中文拎咩？"},{"pid":"496dc6a3634d1b5d0036c620f80a00988a6999bd","tid":445013,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"講黎有咩意思?"},{"pid":